p.k: Gumball and Darwin learn that it isn't wise to upset Hector, Elmore's resident Giant. / Nicole seeks to develop a sense of ambition in Gumball / When everyone in the Watterson household wants to watch their favourite show at the same time, a massive fight breaks out over control of the television remote. / Gumball is determined to drive Penny away from Leslie / Gumball seeks justice when Banana Joe chews Darwin's pen.
